			<h3><a href="/en/Blogs/Judith-s-blog">Judith’s blog</a></h3>
		</div>
		<div class="box-content">
						<ul>
							<li>
										<a href="/en/Blogs/Judith-s-blog/Judith-s-pick-March-2015">
											<i>Blog post:</i> Judith's pick - March 2015
						<span class="tagline">(12/03/2015)</span>
					</a>
